targets.query:
from(bucket: "EUCBrokerComparison")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> group(columns: ["_field"])
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Solution"] =~ /^${Solution:regex}$/ )
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["NC2_Validated"] =~ /^${NC2_Validated:regex}$/ )
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Broker_Placement"] =~ /^${Broker_Placement:regex}$/ )
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Protocol"] =~ /^${Protocol:regex}$/ )
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Element"] =~ /^${PE_Integration:regex}$/ )
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["Central"] =~ /^${PC_Integration:regex}$/ )
  |> sort()
  |> yield(name: "sort")
